# NOTICE

## Project Background

This Splunk Technology Add-on for eMASS (TA-suhlabs-eMASS) is provided as an 
open-source contribution to benefit U.S. Government programs and agencies that 
require integration between eMASS (Enterprise Mission Assurance Support Service) 
and Splunk for security compliance monitoring.

## Development History

Initial development of this software began during government-funded hours. 
Subsequent enhancements, optimizations, and maintenance have been performed 
by the author on their own personal time without government compensation.

